stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Draft: "Save draft"
    Draft --> Published: "Publish when required fields pass"
    Published --> Published: "Update published content"
    Published --> Draft: "Unpublish only if policy/implementation supports"
    Published --> Archived: "Archive when collection adds explicit archive state"
    Archived --> [*]

    note right of Draft
      Canonical workflow hiện tại là Payload drafts.
      Không giả định approval nhiều bước nếu repo chưa có.
    end note

    note right of Published
      publishedAt là timestamp public delivery.
      Search sync và revalidation là downstream async.
    end note
